 a better choice, but \"layered\narchitecture\" outperforms if PCM write performance can be significantly\nimproved in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2016 01:10:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Sep 2016 07:28:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-03"}
