istic iron\nL-peak appears. On the other hand, just below the iron K-edge, the optical\ndepth is the lowest and the RMS spectrum has a broad dip.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2016 13:27:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-07"}
